Deploy apps with Helm using terraform

Step 1: Setup your machine(with minikube) or Kubernetes GKE cluster

Step 2: Install and configure Helm

Step 3: Configure Service Account on GKE

Step 4: Prep Helm Charts
        helm create wordpress-chart
        
Step 4:Applying Terraform Configuration.
       Terraform init,apply
       
Step 5: Execute kubectl get svc to get the IP address of your endpoint.

Your application is now deployed! Check it out and confirm that the deployment was successful
